      <description>&lt;p&gt;We can make a new data type that strips leading and trailing spaces from input fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34;&gt;mkdir app/types
touch app/types/string_stripped_type.rb
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
